                 TOPIC 5 â€” KADANE'S ALGORITHM
            â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• -->
            <div class="topic-card" id="tp5">
                <div class="topic-header">
                    <div class="topic-num">05</div>
                    <div style="flex:1">
                        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
                            <div class="topic-title">Kadane's Algorithm</div>
                            <span class="tier-badge tier-T1">Algorithms</span>
                            <span class="topic-type">Technique Â· DP</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="topic-meta">28 problems Â· max subarray, circular, product, deletion, 2D, tree variants</div>
                    </div>
