                    <div class="info-box"><strong>ðŸ”§ #9 â€” Minimum Sum Subarray:</strong> Given integer array nums, find the minimum sum of any non-empty contiguous subarray. Constraints: 1 â‰¤ n â‰¤ 10âµ, âˆ’10â´ â‰¤ nums[i] â‰¤ 10â´. Example: [2,âˆ’3,4,âˆ’1,âˆ’2] â†’ âˆ’3. Key Insight: Replace max with min in every comparison; init minEndingHere = nums[0]; start loop at index 1.</div>
