                 TOPIC 6 â€” MERGE INTERVALS (MASTERY)
            â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• -->
            <div class="topic-card" id="tp6">
                <div class="topic-header">
                    <div class="topic-num">06</div>
                    <div style="flex:1">
                        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
                            <div class="topic-title">Merge Intervals</div>
                            <span class="tier-badge tier-T1">Algorithms</span>
                            <span class="topic-type">Greedy Â· Sweep Â· DP Â· Segment Tree</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="topic-meta">37 problems Â· merge, insert, sweep, coverage, weighted DP, online CRUD, 2-D, circular</div>
