  â†’ YES: Weighted Job Scheduling DP (#17).

<strong>Q5:</strong> Do you need to COUNT something (rooms, overlaps, groups)?
  â†’ YES: Sweep-line with +1/âˆ’1 events OR min-heap of end-times (#6, #13).
  â†’ NO:  Q6.

<strong>Q6:</strong> Do you need to REMOVE intervals (minimise overlaps)?
  â†’ YES: Greedy Activity Selection â€” sort by end (#3, #7).
  â†’ NO:  Q7.

<strong>Q7:</strong> Do you need COVERAGE (cover a target range with fewest intervals)?
  â†’ YES: Greedy interval covering â€” sort by start, extend reach (#33).
  â†’ NO:  GAPS? â†’ Gap detection (#11, #12).
