if cur[0] &lt;= end:</code></pre>
                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 3 â€” Sorting by wrong key (start vs end)</strong><br>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG for Activity Selection (Non-overlapping Intervals)
