                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 5 â€” Meeting Rooms II: push without popping (room not reused)</strong><br>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: allocates new room even when one is free
