                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 7 (Stage 3) â€” 2D difference array: missing the (+v) at (r2+1, c2+1)</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: only three of the four corners updated
