                        <tr><td>3</td><td>"Extend to 2D: count submatrices with sum = target."</td><td>Fix two row boundaries (O(nÂ²)), reduce to 1D subarray-sum-equals-K on column prefix sums. O(nÂ²m).</td></tr>
