                        <tbody>
                        <tr><td>5</td><td>"The array has only 0s and 1s. Count subarrays with equal 0s and 1s."</td><td>Transform: 0â†’âˆ’1, 1â†’+1. Count subarrays with sum=0. Now it's a Stage 2 problem.</td></tr>
