                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 2 (Stage 2) â€” Duplicate skipping: wrong condition (across-levels instead of same-level)</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: skips valid elements when previous sibling was used at a DIFFERENT level
