    continue</code></pre>
                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 3 (Stage 2) â€” Permutations with duplicates: wrong used-array condition</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: skips too aggressively â€” misses valid permutations
