    continue</code></pre>
                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 4 (Stage 2) â€” Combination sum: no termination on negative remaining</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: recurses indefinitely when remaining &lt; 0
