# FIX: add early termination
    if remaining &lt; 0: return
    if remaining == 0: result.append(path[:]); return</code></pre>
                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 5 (Stage 3) â€” Grid backtracking: forgetting to unmark visited cell</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: cells remain marked, blocking future valid paths
