                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 6 (Stage 3) â€” N-Queens: wrong diagonal encoding</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: (row, col) tuple is not the diagonal invariant
