                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 8 (Stage 4) â€” Expression Add Operators: multiply without adjusting last term</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: multiply applied to cumulative sum, not just the last term
backtrack(pos+length, cur * num, num)  # cur is wrong base for multiply
# FIX: track `last` (the last operand added) separately
