                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 9 (Stage 5) â€” Memoisation with mutable path in state key</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: tuple(path) includes accumulation which varies â€” wrong key
