                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 10 (Stage 5) â€” Bitmask: using OR to "undo" instead of XOR or AND-NOT</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: OR cannot undo a set bit
mask |= (1 &lt;&lt; i)  # set bit
# ... recurse ...
