                        <tr><td>5</td><td>"How would you solve Sudoku faster than pure backtracking?"</td><td>Constraint propagation (AC-3 / arc consistency): after placing a digit, propagate to all related cells; reduces branching factor from 9 to ~2â€“3 on average.</td></tr>
