                        Stage 1/2: under 12 min. Stage 3: under 20 min. Stage 4: under 35 min. <em>Exchange argument drill:</em> for every problem solved, write the 3-step argument in under 3 minutes â€” your interview proof. <em>Sort-key drill:</em> given a problem, identify the sort key in under 60 seconds before writing code â€” the sort key IS the solution. <em>Anti-greedy recognition:</em> for trap problems (S.No 30â€“32), identify in under 30 seconds WHY greedy fails and what replaces it.<br><br>
