dp[0] = True</code></pre>
                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 2 (Stage 2) â€” House Robber: dp initialised to nums only</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: ignores that house 0 alone might be better
