                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 3 (Stage 2) â€” 0/1 Knapsack: forward iteration causes item reuse</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: forward loop â†’ same item used multiple times
