                    </div>
                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 4 (Stage 2) â€” Circular House Robber: single DP on full array</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: first and last house can both be robbed
