                    <div class="warn-box"><strong>Bug 5 (Stage 2) â€” Coin Change: dp initialised to infinity for dp[0]</strong>
                        <pre style="white-space:pre-wrap;margin:.4rem 0"><code># BUG: dp[0]=inf â†’ dp[coin]=inf+1 â†’ wrong
